[{"url_token": "gong-cao-28", "headline": "懒、宅", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636579745", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "636579745", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>关于打灯并线的，我难道是异类？你不打灯就并线，我百分百是不让的，而且99%的概率您还真加不进来。但如果你打灯，并且确实没有同时强行并线的动作，我倒真的会让你一下。</p>", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "弓草", "author_id": "d4a4e578aa4691bfaee244a3c32882f2", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "gong-cao-28", "headline": "懒、宅", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637623140", "reply_comment_id": "636659563", "reply_root_comment_id": "636579745", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>惭愧，哪儿是什么老司机，2000年拿的本，不过正式开车是两年半前找陪练后才开始。平时开个小飞度，可能这车比较小吧，所以刚上路的时候很多车都喜欢强行加在我前面，被“欺负”的时间长了，跟车技术，尤其是在堵车时跟车的技术就这么被迫训练出来了。</p><p>其实路上心态好的司机也有很多，刚上路的时候，有的路段是我必须要并线了，我就打灯，是有很多车像你说的一样马上提速不让我加，但我就耐心等，打着灯等个几辆十几辆甚至二十几辆总有好心的司机不忍心了，就会让我加进去。当然现在不需要这么傻等，也会找合适的机会并线，但肯定也是先打灯，并且确定对方让我加，我才真的并线。</p>", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "弓草", "author_id": "d4a4e578aa4691bfaee244a3c32882f2", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636659563", "reply_comment_id": "636579745", "reply_root_comment_id": "636579745", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "正好相反，如果都是您这样的好心态老司机，就好了。我感觉很多时候就是有的车在后面慢悠悠，我提前打灯想变道，后车就赶紧狂按喇叭加速不让我超。所以后来我就看，有并线距离了，先把车头打过来，然后在打灯，后车反而不按喇叭了。当然，插队变道总是不好。", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "vzcsd", "headline": "IT", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "765093111", "reply_comment_id": "636659563", "reply_root_comment_id": "636579745", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "不是说你打灯就必须要让你懂不懂，别人不让你就是应该等，而不是去抢", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "隔壁", "author_id": "cd017be6cfd8701fe5e7d463aa4bcb01", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "kuo-ran-wu-lei-40", "headline": "设计师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636242448", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "636242448", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "锁车那条太魔性[捂脸][捂脸][捂脸]", "like_count": 5, "author_name": "廓然无累", "author_id": "dcc496728a5411fb5a0248addfaf45c0", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636391354", "reply_comment_id": "636242448", "reply_root_comment_id": "636242448", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "千万次的回头才换来的一条总结[捂脸][捂脸]", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "644280079", "reply_comment_id": "643487976", "reply_root_comment_id": "636242448", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "一般能想到的应该是锁了啊，莫非您就是传说中的？……", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "luo-zhi-xiang-55-90", "headline": "你看不见我(●′ω`●) ", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "643487976", "reply_comment_id": "636391354", "reply_root_comment_id": "636242448", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>然而我每次回头都是忘记锁</p><a class=\"comment_sticker\" href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-12562ad40366818a1ea39bcecb2599a0.gif\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\">[害羞]</a>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "我不是罗志祥", "author_id": "cc5a49292427ccda9279e010ffeb1f72", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "chen-yun-54-40-72", "headline": "就事论事，有理有节", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637072069", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "637072069", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "想法不一样，如果我个人买，内饰在我选车最多只能排到第三位，不能再高了！我首选动力，其次操控和底盘质感，再次考虑内饰、配置那些。三大件给我的感受才是最关键的", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "cycloud", "author_id": "c99596493c9d8b463c7247b2a77635df", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637491693", "reply_comment_id": "637072069", "reply_root_comment_id": "637072069", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "确实追求的都不一样，我有一个朋友就喜欢开快的，08年卡罗拉都是地板油180跟别人飚。他说他有钱就买320i，我说太小了，以后有孩子不划算，他不听，我俩还吵了一架[大笑][大笑]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "nan-nan-zhu-73", "headline": "设计师", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "632893308", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "632893308", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>大哥我也是红色POLO。现在10万公里了。</p>", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "楠楠丶", "author_id": "8e54a1af1b75d495e783b35f5c7bf483", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "634280775", "reply_comment_id": "632893308", "reply_root_comment_id": "632893308", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "老司机握爪，这款当时老骚气了", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "xiangbin-26", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "632614776", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "632614776", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "路虎哪一款，多少钱？", "like_count": 4, "author_name": "不说话只看戏", "author_id": "be753ac133e732a2f13db190f6bb7368", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636393813", "reply_comment_id": "632614776", "reply_root_comment_id": "632614776", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "神行，价格随便查的到~~", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "wan-ju-xiong-27-43", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636380485", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "636380485", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有个聪明的变速箱也很重要，你开过君威应该懂[捂脸]", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "逍遥白翎", "author_id": "264ed39ca51bafbf197c1be5d187fd93", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636391026", "reply_comment_id": "636380485", "reply_root_comment_id": "636380485", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "别提了，都是泪[捂脸][捂脸][捂脸]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "ericfan-93", "headline": "永远保持好奇心", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636214153", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "636214153", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "对买丐版不太认同，除了三大，还有很多其他是改不了的。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "御风精灵", "author_id": "4e14e63f9b585d435aaa40f60963402a", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "ericfan-93", "headline": "永远保持好奇心", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637085534", "reply_comment_id": "636393551", "reply_root_comment_id": "636214153", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有些配置，尤其是重要配置不是加装能搞定的。比如安全气囊，比如盲点监测，还有天窗这些。有些即使加装有什么隐患完全不知道。而加装的钱也不一定比直接上高配少，却要操很多心。还要单风险。所以究竟买什么配置的车还要看增加的钱得到了什么。", "like_count": 3, "author_name": "御风精灵", "author_id": "4e14e63f9b585d435aaa40f60963402a", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "sunsik", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "738110725", "reply_comment_id": "636393551", "reply_root_comment_id": "636214153", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "重要的一些安排配置是加不了的，舒适性配置其实不太重要", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "sunsik", "author_id": "bff21338fb3340956e6abc42acc8f6c1", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ericfan-93", "headline": "永远保持好奇心", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637658575", "reply_comment_id": "637562013", "reply_root_comment_id": "636214153", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "这种情况不能一概而论了，有人喜欢低调点，有人喜欢讲面子。如果品牌的权重比较大，也可以考虑贷款买更合适的配置。都是未来花钱。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "御风精灵", "author_id": "4e14e63f9b585d435aaa40f60963402a", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636393551", "reply_comment_id": "636214153", "reply_root_comment_id": "636214153", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "很多是可以加的。我记得13年我刚买君威，一个客户在高配迈腾和低配A4中徘徊。我说买迈腾，啥功能都有，倒车影像翻牌很有逼格。最后买了。然后现在还是后悔想买奥迪。当时我也认为高配迈腾啥都有。现在想，忽视了品牌影响力，虽然A4低配，但是总归奥迪。其他能用到的配置可以加钱，但牌子变不了~~现在改装老厉害了，我微信一个改奔驰的，从液晶屏到尾箱移动升降一套带走，不留遗憾[大笑][大笑]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637562013", "reply_comment_id": "636214153", "reply_root_comment_id": "636214153", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "如果钱只够买你想买的品牌的低配咋办呢？", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "huang-guo-35", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "636445954", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "636445954", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "衣服也是这样吧 都是给别人看的  三 鞋舒不舒服只有脚知道。买车内饰比外观重要。你到最后才会发现，内饰好看，用着舒服是最重要的，外观是别人看的，内饰才是自己享受的。这也是我一直非常喜欢奔驰的内饰的原因。记得北野武坐出租车看朋友开自己的法拉利的故事，就和我们看不到自己开车的帅劲儿的一样的感觉。", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "黄果", "author_id": "e6dd9738568d34d89ba1aa31c8537a01", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "guan-lei-62", "headline": "还是个年轻人", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "733047857", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "733047857", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有些真的说出我的习惯！在大多数答主那里都没看到的！<br>对了，如果跟着大车不小心闯了红灯，收到违章通知，是可以申诉的。", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "关三石", "author_id": "f84dea3270bedfc5b328843802b5a5ac", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "chen-yun-54-40-72", "headline": "就事论事，有理有节", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637073870", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "637073870", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "当然，动力要包含与变速箱的匹配，不仅仅是光发动机的参数高", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "cycloud", "author_id": "c99596493c9d8b463c7247b2a77635df", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "missyou4", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "637490853", "reply_comment_id": "637073870", "reply_root_comment_id": "637073870", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "动力和变速箱匹配真的重要。记得最初的科鲁兹的匹配大问题，就是白瞎了发动机", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "Missyou4", "author_id": "e2e837a44a0523bec13b3e7ea472b13e", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}]